 of Hisham ibn al-Mughirah have sought my permission to marry their daughters to Ali ibn Abi Talib. I do not give permission, again, I do not give\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/ali-sabr-iman-head-body\/","url_meta":{"origin":19501,"position":1},"title":"Ali on Sabr: Patience to faith like a head to a body","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Masruq reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, patience is to faith as the head is to the body. If the head is cut, the body will perish.\u201d Then, Ali raised his voice and he said, \u201cNo doubt, there is no faith for one\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9897,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/22\/ali-ibn-abi-talib-harun-musa\/","url_meta":{"origin":19501,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Prophets: Ali is to Muhammad as Aaron to Moses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, set out to Tabuk and he left Ali behind. Ali said, \"You leave me behind with the women and children?\" The Prophet said, \"Are you not pleased in the same position for me as Aaron\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8246,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/ali-doing-spreading-fahishah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19501,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Sin: Doing and spreading vulgarity equal in sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Hassan ibn Kurayb reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cOne who says something vulgar and one who publicizes it are equal in sin.\" Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 324 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/ali-ibn-abu-talib-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":19501,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Curses: Those who curse others are themselves cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubayd al-Kindi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThose who curse others are themselves cursed.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 315 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u064a\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0646\u062f\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u200f \u0639\u0644\u064a \u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0637\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u200f \u0644\u064f\u0639\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0639\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064e 315 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062f\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0641\u0631\u062f \u0644\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0628\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34241,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/06\/ali-do-not-rebuke\/","url_meta":{"origin":19501,"position":5},"title":"Ali on Blame: Do not excessively rebuke people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abi al-Sa\u2019ib reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cDo not frequently scold others, for scolding leads to resentment and hatred and too much of it is bad manners.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-\u2018Uqala\u0304\u2019 1\/182 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0628\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064c \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u